Package: brfutures
Type: Package
Title: Brazilian Futures Data Tools
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Hugo",
    family = "Rzepian Teixeira",
    email = "hugorteixeira@senhormercado.com.br",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lightweight tools to download, parse, cache, and retrieve B3
    (BM&F Bovespa) futures daily bulletins using only the public HTML endpoint.
    Provides update helpers that keep a local cache in sync and fast accessors
    for cached contract data.
